This is the xml_decoder-write-a-block package meant as a guide to building
out-of-tree packages. To use the xml_decoder blocks, the Python namespaces
is in 'xml_decoder', which is imported as:

    import xml_decoder

See the Doxygen documentation for details about the blocks available
in this package. A quick listing of the details can be found in Python
after importing by using:

    help(xml_decoder)
